Simple app to create coloring pictures. Requres the himage library to run.

How to build:

Native

Just invoke cmake, eg:

mkdir build
cd build
ccmake .. (enter the required paths)
make -j<number of jobs>


Emscripten

Use the emscripten cmake wrapper: emcmake ccmake ..

Then use emrun to start the webserver: emrun decolorizer.html